summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Alder Street from 32" Avenue to 33" Avenue, et al, in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 21725, creating Local Improvement District No. 2166 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
